citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany the APHIS Official during the inspection process at 2:30 pm on July
26, 2023.
The licensee's son told me that she was not home and he did not know what time she would return. I left message on
licensee's cell phone and she returned my call about 4 hours later.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany the APHIS Official during the inspection process at 2:30 pm on July 
26, 2023. 
 
The licensee's son told me that she was not home and he did not know what time she would return. I left message on 
licensee's cell phone and she returned my call about 4 hours later. 
 
 
End Section
